OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells at first.
OL,7,FBecoming cloudier in the west with the
OL,8,Fodd light shower, staying dry with
OL,9,Fsome clear spells in the east. Winds
OL,10,Fgradually ease.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMostly dry in the east with
OL,13,Fsunny spells and variable cloud.
OL,14,FCloudier in the west with a few light
OL,15,Fshowers. Some rain spreads east in the
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
