OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fchangeable, often cloudy and windy few
OL,7,Fdays with spells of rain, occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy and persistent in the west. Best
OL,9,Fof the drier, brighter spells around
OL,10,Fthe Moray Firth.
